Kipi-plugins 4.0.0 - Release date: 2014/01/12
------------------------------------------------------------------------

NEW FEATURES:

General  : New tool to export collection to Google Drive cloud service.
General  : New tool to export collection to DropBox cloud service.

MediaWiki: allow removal of metadata/GPS coordinates before uploading.
MediaWiki: graphical interface improvements.

BUGFIXES FROM KDE BUGZILLA (alias B.K.O | http://bugs.kde.org):

001 ==> 319664 - kipi-plugins 3.2.0-beta2 (and 3.1.0) installs a static archive /usr/lib64/libPropertyBrowser.a.
002 ==> 324044 - MediaWiki: Fix bug, add feature, improve usability
003 ==> 307689 - digiKam crashes during Export to Rajce service [patch].
004 ==> 323118 - SmugMug API access fails after SmugMug relaunch [patch].
005 ==> 324646 - digiKam hangs when producting "Video Slide Show" [patch].
006 ==> 319611 - Invalid placement of TimeStamp element in kml export [patch].
007 ==> 319612 - Update kml export to use KML 2.2 schema [patch].
008 ==> 199978 - Can not email images on Windows [patch].
009 ==> 320782 - Try to automatically guess new flickr set name from image folders [patch].
010 ==> 326728 - Panorama Stitching crashes upon start.
011 ==> 300445 - Kipi integration with cloud storage (as Dropbox or GDrive) for quick sharing.
